description: UNIQUE TWO BED PENTHOUSE WITH LOFT AND MASSIVE DEEDED ROOFDECK! UNIT OFFERINGS INCLUDE A LARGE OPEN FLOORPLAN, A WELL-APPOINTED KITCHEN WITH GRANITE COUNTERTOPS COMPLETE WITH ISLAND, DESIGNATED DINING AREA AND LARGE LIVING ROOM WITH WOOD-BURNING FIREPLACE. FRONT FACING OFFICE WITH EXPOSED BRICK AND SPIRAL STAIRCASE LEADING TO LIGHT FILLED LOFT AREA WITH SKYLIGHTS! THIS TRANSITIONAL FLOOR PLAN OFFERS KING AND QUEEN SIZED BEDROOMS AND TWO OVERSIZED STONE BATHS. ADDITIONAL FEATURES INCLUDE NEW ROOF AND ROOFDECK, FRESH PAINT THROUGHOUT, NEWLY CARPETED BEDROOMS, HARDWOOD FLOORS, LAUNDRY IN THE BUILDING, AND LOW HOA FEES! CONVENIENTLY SITUATED ALONG THE BUS ROUTE, ACROSS FROM HUNTER’S AND FAT BABY, AND JUST TWO BLOCKS AWAY FROM ALL OF THE RESTAURANTS/BARS THAT WEST BROADWAY HAS TO OFFER
